They're needed to channel the ancient moogle magic, you see.
You'll also have to accumulate ≺Numeric Parameter 0≻ merit point≺Singular/Plural Choice (Parameter 0)≻[/s] to provide the necessary energy to trigger the reaction, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

I'll be sittin' this one out, I fear.
I may have mastered the martial arts, but I know better than to get mixed up with moogle mumbo-jumbo. Heh heh heh...
Now go get 'em!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Say it ain't so, kupo!
Ah, but it is not a moogle's place to question the judgment of an accomplished adventurer such as yourself.
Come back if you ever have a change of heart.≺Prompt≻

My wings are aflutter with anticipation!≺Prompt≻

Yoo-hoooooo! Mister Magian Moogle man!

What is it this time?

I'd call you by your proper name if you'd actually tell anyone what it is!
But nooo, the Magian Mooglehood must ever be shrouded in secrecy, kupo...≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: !?≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
My world was tipped upside down.
I was suddenly able to read people's thoughts and, just like Cardinal Mildaurion, I never aged another day.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
So that is what happened.
You were the Keeper of the Apocalypse...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
But things are different now.
You are no longer the one, are you?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Are you saying that nothing has changed? What is to happen to Prishe?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Judging by the actions of Bahamut, the keeper is still among us.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But over the last twenty years I have watched over the lands of Vana'diel, I have seen no other possible incarnations...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Bahamut wishes to see me smashed to bits in the form of the Twilight God.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It was Diabolos that let me in on my destiny as the Keeper of the Apocalypse.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is my fate to be destroyed along with this magicite, and set adrift from the cycle of the mothercrystal.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: No! This is too horrible!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Listen to me, Ulmia.
We've come pretty far in this quest.
I've already heard four of the verses needed to resurrect the Twilight God.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Once we have the last verse, we can finally stand before Bahamut...!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Please, Prishe!
Do you hear what you are saying!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
How can I let you offer your very existence to Promathia?
There must be another way...!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Calm yourself, Ulmia.
Prishe will not be coming with us.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The last verse of the “Memoria de la S^tona” no longer exists, and there is no weapon left to battle the Twilight God.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Pitting the full force of Jeuno against the wyrms is our only recourse.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There is no other way to save the children of Altana from extinction.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But Miss Mildaurion! What about me?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Lady Esha'ntarl!
The Jeunoan Armada is prepared for battle!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I must go.
Beyond the sea of endless clouds.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Cardinal Mildaurion!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Prishe. Ulmia.
It is only a matter of time until Jeuno becomes a war zone.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I will prepare an airship for your return to Tavnazia.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Protect that which is most dear to you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Dammit!
There's no way in hell it's ending this way!
It's time to put it all on the line!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Prishe!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻!
Ulmia!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I know you guys can do it!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You're strong enough now to beat the hell out of me when I become Promathia...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Listen, there is someone in Selbina who knows the fifth verse.
Her memory is a little shoddy, though...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Find the fifth verse!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I need you to do this!
You hear me!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I cannot...!
Prishe, wait!≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Ulmia, I have heard the entire story.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Louverance!?≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
This must be the guidance of Altana.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
And I also happen to possess the means to revive her past.
Let us be on our way.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What?
Is there a girl in Selbina with a serious case of amnesia?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
How would I know? I'm always confined to my post here in Jeuno.
You're the adventurer. Why don't you know these things?≺Prompt≻

The attack against Bahamut failed, but we have dealt him a critical blow.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Lady Esha'ntarl is to join the main fleet and lead our forces in a mass assault.≺Prompt≻

She mentioned that she would like to meet with you all before the attack commences.
You are to meet her for a confidential briefing in the tavern in Upper Jeuno.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
Do not keep Lady Esha'ntarl waiting.
May victory in battle be yours.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

The palace is often the site for grand banquets that are attended by dignitaries from every nation.
In times like these, we do our utmost to see that the needs of our important visitors are met.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Recently, ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 0)≻[Lord Nag'molada/Lady Esha'ntarl] has been requesting the oddest things from the palace staff.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: These requests appear to be for objects desired by guests of the Duchy.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: These requests appear to be for objects desired by guests of our eminent official.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If the requested items could be found in Jeuno, nay, in the markets of any country, we would endeavor to procure them.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
However, many of these objects are not available for purchase.
I am in quite a quandary, as you can see.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The Empty are a cold and hollow species--their very existence a void of nothingness.
They possess no feeling, no will, no purpose... It is this lack of characteristics that makes them powerful, as they have no known weaknesses.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: However, deep within their dark shells we have discovered that something does exist--that “something” being a fragment of a memory lost in the pages of time.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If you happen to have the fortune of coming across one of these incomplete memories on your journeys, bring it to me and I shall purify it into a form known as “anima” using the methods discovered by the society.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: By studying the various types of memories left by the Empty, we may be able to discover their strengths and weaknesses.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
What is a Diorama?
Similar to the one used in the popular children's board game “Battleista,” Diorama Abdhaljs is a miniature version of an actual location in Vana'diel.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: However, there is one thing that sets Diorama Abdhaljs apart from its counterpart. In the place of wooden game pieces, living, breathing warriors are used!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: How is that possible, you ask? Well, in his studies, my master was able to unlock the secrets of the ancient magic known as “Mini”--a forbidden spell with the power to reduce objects to a fraction of their original size.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: By using the incantations inscribed on codices authored by Abdhaljs, players can be temporarily shrunk down and teleported to the miniature battlefield hidden on a secluded island somewhere in the Tavnazian Archipelago.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is all perfectly safe, and the all-seeing Abdhaljs guarantees that you will be satisfied with your experience within his creation (though no refunds will be offered if you are not).≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Come to think of it, I knew that ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Mr./Ms.]...≺Player Name≻...yes, ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Mr./Ms.] ≺Player Name≻'s team would win all along! field.Element:Text: Ahem! Anyway, now let me present you with your prize and a new title. I'm looking forward to seeing your name in my register again in the near future! Au Revoir!≺Prompt≻

I knew that you were talented, but it looks like you also had a smite of fortune on your side.
How much did you pay off Lady Luck to have her smile down on only you?
Hah hah hah... I'm sorry. That wasn't very funny...≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: But seriously, the blood you spilled, the tears you shed, the sweat you...you...sweat--all of these made you and your companions that much stronger. It was truly your hard work and perserverance that lead you to victory. Though, I knew all along that your team would win.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
Out of my...
Wait just a moment. Let me have a good look at you...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Yes...
You may be of some use to me after all.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My name is Venessa. I have traveled from my homeland far to the west to hone my skills under the supervision of the ducal alchemists.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I am currently studying the phenomenon known as the “Emptiness” and how its byproducts can be better utilized in my field.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My recent research has shown that in addition to the variety of creatures that roam the plains of Promyvion, there are a handful of even stronger manifests that dwell deep within towers that loom above the vast expanses of darkness.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
To continue my work, I require fresh remnants of these rare beasts.
Of course, your efforts will not go unrewarded.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Will you accept my offer?
≺Selection Dialog≻Of course.
Not today.
Tell me more.
You've lost me.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Then you are wasting my time.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I have told you enough!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Then you are of no use to me. Begone!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Excellent.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: According to data collected by the Duchy, there are several different locations around Vana'diel where the Empty thrive. Adventurers have given these realms the name “Promyvion.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If my hypothesis is correct, I believe there are four types of special remnants--one to coincide with each area. Which area do you wish to investigate?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Travel to...
≺Selection Dialog≻Nowhere at this time.
The Spire of Holla.
The Spire of Dem.
The Spire of Mea.
The Spire of Vahzl.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If you have no intentions of assisting me, then stop wasting my time!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 1)≻[Holla/Dem/Mea/Vahzl], you say?
Then you will need this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3ｂ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Wait just a moment... I remember you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: While I appreciate your assistance, I do not have any more censers to aid you on your travels into Promyvion. I must ask you to return at a later date.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yes, I may be able to provide you with another ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3ｂ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ on ≺Unknown Parameter (Type: AC) 4≻ (≺Unknown Parameter (Type: AB) 4≻ Earth time) and not a day sooner.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Here, you may have this one, but take care not to lose it. These artifacts are extremely difficult to come by, and I have only a limited supply.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And if you happen to come across one of the rare remnants that I seek, bring it directly to me. Only then will you receive your reward.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What is this? You say you found something that may be of interest?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Yes... Yes!
With this I can prove my ability to the society! I am guaranteed a position within their ranks for sure!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hm? Your reward? Oh, I do remember promising you something if you succeeded at your mission.
How about this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻#≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻? I don't think the society will be missing it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Out of my...
Wait just a moment. You wouldn't happen to have returned because you wish to delve into the depths of Promyvion once more, would you?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Well?
≺Selection Dialog≻That's why I'm here.
I was just passing by.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I have neither the time nor patience to be bothered by every ignorant cretin that happens to wander by. Begone!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻!
Lady Esha'ntarl's ship has returned.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
This is excellent timing.
I was ordered to find you and ask that you proceed to the Marble Bridge--the tavern in Upper Jeuno.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
My duty here is done.
I must now journey to each nation and report that the Wyrmking Bahamut no longer poses a threat.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I hear that this development is all thanks to you and your companions.
You have the gratitude of all Jeunoans.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I have awaited your return, ≺Player Name≻.
You must tell me all that has happened.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: After clashing with our army several times, the dragons suddenly broke off their attack and disappeared into the distant clouds.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There were voices raised in support of hunting the wyrms into extinction, but for the moment we have returned to resupply and reconsider our position.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Now that you are here, I can finally be certain.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Am I to assume from your jubilant features that the Keeper of the Apocalypse has been defeated?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Has the keeper been defeated?
≺Selection Dialog≻Completely.
Who can say?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I knew it!
Bahamut sensed the keeper's downfall and pulled his forces out of battle...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Tell me.
What momentous events transpired in the Celestial Capital?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: On Cape Riverne, the images that flowed into me from Selh'teus...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: They were of the incomplete Paradise, Al'Taieu...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The people of Al'Taieu returned to their deity ten thousand years ago.
Returned to Promathia...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Opening the Gates of Paradise” is a metaphor for restoring the shattered mothercrystal.
A way to return the world to its original state.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The world becomes a paradise, and its people ascend to godhood.
The Dawnmaiden Yve'noile has memories of witnessing the true form of the great goddess Altana.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yve'noile spoke to me before we parted ways.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: She said, “As I gazed upon her perfection, I realized I could not be a part of her. I wondered who I could possibly be.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That was when she began her research into the race of people.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: After shifting her focus to the inexplicable appearance of the Kuluu phenomenon, Yve'noile became aware of the darkness that resided within us all.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Her realization led her to betray the king and his son, and adamantly oppose any plan to open the Gates of Paradise.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: She had discovered our origins as the children of Promathia...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But all has not been resolved.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The Emptiness still seethes within the mothercrystals.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And the surviving Zilart yet cling desperately to their shadowy plan of returning to Paradise.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I gave up my life in Tavnazia almost thirty years ago to infiltrate the organization of the newly awakened Zilart.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But I have been unable to stem their vast power on my own.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: However, we now have a common enemy in the Emptiness. For a time, the people of this age will require the aid of the ancients.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The ancients, too, will need your continuing help.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Surely the Dawn Maiden has bequeathed something of value to her younger kin.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I will find out what this may be, and speak with Archduke Kam'lanaut. He will heed my words.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I shall continue to watch over the world that you and your companions have fought so valiantly to protect.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Now that Nag'molada is gone and the wyrms have ceased their attacks, it is time to remind the Zilart of their true responsibility:≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The safety of the mothercrystals and the battle against the Emptiness.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I will continue to monitor their actions as I watch over the world that you and your companions have fought so valiantly to protect.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There is one thing I'd like you to keep in mind, ≺Player Name≻.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You were able to save the world and her people without sacrificing one or the other.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But do not misunderstand.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This possibility did not always exist.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It was only with the strength and faith of many people that such a path could open before you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I have left with the owner of this tavern three rewards that may help you on your adventures.
Feel free to choose one.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Until our paths cross once more, ≺Player Name≻.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thank you, and farewell.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

It's surprising to find a Zilartian with a level head on her shoulders.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There are four mothercrystal locations: the Crag of Holla, the Crag of Dem, the Crag of Mea, and the ruins of Pso'Xja.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Our investigation into the Emptiness surrounding these locations has produced some unusual readings.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We put together a research team equipped with the latest weapons--weapons designed to combat the Emptiness--and sent them to Pso'Xja.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And you wouldn't guess who they encountered...≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
The ruins of Pso'Xja are under Tenshodo authority.

field.Element:Text: Verena had wandered down there like she was being guided by something.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I found this at the place to where I was drawn.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Apparently it belonged to a Galka known as Raogrimm--I'm sure you remember the name.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Verena was once the receptacle for the memories of the Shadow Lord.
This must be the reason behind her behavior.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Similar readings have been recorded from the Emptiness found below the crags of Holla, Dem, and Mea.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We have marked the points where the fluctuations were the strongest.
I would like to entrust the investigation of these areas to you, ≺Player Name≻.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If my intuition on what lies out there is correct, you will make some fascinating discoveries indeed.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You're a brave soul, ≺Player Name≻.
You'll never catch me in that awful place again.
Once is more than enough...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Please be careful.
We'll be praying for your safe return.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So these are what were causing such unusual activity within the Emptiness.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I can feel the aura of those who returned to the mothercrystals...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Nag'molada, Eald'narche, and even Archduke Kam'lanaut...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Could it be possible that these entities are attempting to break back into this world?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Will they return as they once were?

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻.
We must put a stop to this.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: These reincarnations are beings that have chosen--and been chosen by--the Emptiness.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Go. Prepare yourself for battle, then return to me here.
Let us raise the curtain on the final conflict.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I fear their powers will be beyond any race that has walked Vana'diel.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: You hand the three crystal slivers to Esha'ntarl.≺Prompt≻

≺Player Name≻.
Let us discuss what needs to be done.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I have returned from an audience with the Wyrmking.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If the Keeper of the Apocalypse is indeed attempting to cross over into this world, there is but one option left to us.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We force the keeper to appear on our terms.
Then we crush him.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: This was Prishe's original plan.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ulmia will sing the Lay of the Immortals in the presence of the fifth mothercrystal.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The time has finally come to use the completed song--the verses you discovered on your journey.
I have faith that Ulmia can perform the piece with little trouble.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Make your way to the Sealion's Den in Tavnazia.
Al'Taieu beckons once again.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: ≺Player Name≻, I have awaited your arrival.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I always feared that my act of relinquishing the Star of Tavnazia...≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: ...would one day bring the world back to the brink of destruction.≺Prompt≻

But to be completely honest, I am overjoyed that this darkness has given us another chance to meet.
Truly, I am...≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
Prishe!
You stop this nonsense at once!≺Prompt≻

You truly are incorrigible!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

Aw, c'mon, Ulmia!
It's been so long since I've seen ≺Player Name≻.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: A normal reunion would be kinda boring, and I just wanted to spice things up a little...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You were just trying to cover up your own awkwardness!≺Prompt≻

“Don't leave...a hole...half...dug...”≺Prompt≻

I never thought I would don this armor again.

Wow, the whole gang's here.

My apologies...≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 1≻
And my thanks!≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 34) 4≻≺Possible Special Code: 00≻

The time has come.

field.Element:Text: Still making unrealistic wishes, Prishe?≺Possible Special Code: 00≻

Miss Mildaurion!
Aldo!?≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I'm sure you all know Zeid.

I will also fight alongside you.

field.Element:Text: The first to taste the vengeance of the dead!≺Prompt≻

There is only...≺Prompt≻

≺Player Name≻.

field.Element:Text: The world only grows larger the longer we live. New lives are born, and new lands are discovered. There're always new adventures to be had.≺Prompt≻

But you don't gotta rush in, you know?

field.Element:Text: Waiting for you.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: The Near East must be in a dire condition to send mercenary recruiters all the way to Jeuno...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I heard many tales of the Great War from my dear departed father. They all seemed irrelevant to me until now...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I see you've got a Salaheem's Sentinel badge there...

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Maybe the empress of Aht Urhgan is short on devoted subjects...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hm? I see you have one of those brass badges that Salaheem's Sentinels are handing out unauthorized. Let me take a look at it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Interesting. Objects from the Near East seem to shine with a different light.
I've heard that the president of Salaheem's Sentinels is quite tight-fisted, but at least this badge is quite luxurious.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Near Eastern cuisine is all the rage now.
Lately I've been studying up on it to add some spice to the palace banquets.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Near Eastern cooking is considered one of the leading cuisines in Vana'diel, so I am sure the archduke will be most pleased.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Lately, the Empire of Aht Urhgan has been building up her army. That's sure to make waves internationally...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do you think we can continue to preserve friendly relations with all three major nations as the balance of power hangs by a thread?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You have gathered here today at the request of the Kingdom of San d'Oria.
I thank you on behalf of the king.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
This is the first time in history that an emergency summit of this nature has taken place.
The issue I lay before you is beyond the scope of a single nation...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Prince Pieuje!
The adventurer you have permitted to attend the summit has arrived.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thank you for coming, ≺Player Name≻.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Allow me to begin by explaining the events that have led to today's meeting.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It began when ≺Player Name≻, mercenary and adventurer, arrived at the gate of the Chateau d'Oraguille bearing a letter of extreme importance.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The contents of that letter prompted me to call the nations together...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It was penned by a sage known as Raillefal, and described in painstaking detail the current state of Aht Urhgan.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This is the same nation that has the port in a frenzy over mercenary recruitment...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The very same.
I speak of the Near Eastern nation, the Empire of Aht Urhgan.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The Empire!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Aht Urhgan is now under pressure from three separate beastman armies, and Al Zahbi, the mighty capital itself, is in danger of falling.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Great Altana...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The Silent Empire...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It was once called that.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You may have been too young to know this, Your Highness, but the rest of us should remember.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I am aware of the term.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In the time of the Great War, the Empire possessed an army greater than the combined forces of the allied nations.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yet not a single soldier was sent in response to calls for aid...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
My apologies.
You are well versed in history.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But knowing this, you should also know that we have no obligation to lift even a finger for Aht Urhgan, no matter how serious her predicament.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Why, Volker, always so calm and cool.
You've grown hot and bothered, and your speech is most cruel.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You should understand, Doctor Shantotto.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You were there on that battlefield.
Who knows how much suffering could've been avoided if we'd had the help of the Empire...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
On the contrary, my dear musketeer.
We owe them more than you can imagine, I fear.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What do you mean!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Aht Urhgan has taken many countries under her yoke...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A ferocious nation that has even bared fangs at the Far Eastern folk.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Calling the Empire to help in our cause,
would be like freeing us from demons in return for dragon jaws.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That may be true, but even the close relationship Aht Urhgan had with Tavnazia...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That subject is not--≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
...the issue here, I know.
Doctor Shantotto, why did Windurst open Mhaura's port to the Empire?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My nation's actions are none of your concern.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: At least we have a backbone--when will Bastok learn...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You go too far, Doctor Shantotto...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Enough!
I did not call you here to speak of possible troop contributions.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Then why are we here, Your Highness?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Our main concern is the treasure thought to be at the center of this conflict--the Astral Candescence.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Astral Candescence”?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is described as some manner of musical instrument, but apparently is much more than that.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This instrument is said to produce a phenomenon known as the “Astral Wind,” a breeze that blows from an unidentifiable source.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It creates a melody in a timbre unheard by mortal ears...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I'm confused.
How can there be a melody if nothing can be heard...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Astral Wind...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hmph. This is all very unusual, but I'm sure we've all seen stranger things before.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An unidentifiable source...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
In Windurst there is no shortage of magical gadgets.
Pens that write by themselves. Brooms that sweep on command...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A breeze...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I mean, they even have that Cardian band.
That's similar, don't you think, Doctor Shantotto?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Astral...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Wind...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Doctor Shantotto?
Is everything alright?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: !!!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ohohohoho!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
If it's automatic instruments you need,
our children make such things before they learn how to read!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The problem lies in the power of the wind.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The wind?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
It envelops those close by, and fills them with a mysterious strength.
There are few who can resist the lure of this energy.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Even among the beastmen...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If the instrument is that dangerous, why not just give it to the beastmen, or smash it out of hand?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
That is what common sense would tell us.
If it were up to an individual, or even an entire town...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What are you trying to say?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What if that decision lay in the hands of a nation?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Even if it posed a threat to your own citizens, if that treasure could one day be your salvation, would you not choose to protect it?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: How could a mere instrument hold that kind of power...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The sage who composed this letter is afraid...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Afraid that this Astral Candescence will one day be the catalyst for a conflict to rival the Crystal War.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: No!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Prince Pieuje...
As a representative for an entire nation, you would do well not to throw those words around so lightly!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
My apologies.
This is merely based on the conjecture of a sage.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Why don't we have ≺Player Name≻, who has seen and heard these things in person, give us ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[his/her] account?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We cannot make a decision based on this tale alone.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A nation has a responsibility to maintain soldiers and weaponry for the defense of its people.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And for a city in this situation, I would go so far as to say that some sort of secret weapon is almost a necessity.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In any case, it doesn't seem that this Astral Candescence presents any immediate danger to the people of Al Zahbi.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I wouldn't say that was entirely true,
if you were me, and I were you.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻.

field.Element:Text: I wish to hear your honest opinion.≺Prompt≻

Give Pieuje your honest opinion?
≺Selection Dialog≻Yes.

I rely upon your vast experience as an adventurer.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: What is the Astral Candescence?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If it is such an important treasure, then why not secret it away inside the palace instead of placing it in the area most vulnerable to beastman attacks?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I sense some hidden purpose for this dangerous object...≺Prompt≻

The Walahra Philosophy...

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻.
If you have nothing to contribute, then there is little point in you being here...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Sage Walahra?
What manner of person is this?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...I see.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The father of the Walahra Philosophy and an alchemist of great renown...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “I, alone, do not possess all the answers. Let us ponder the mysteries of the universe together.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Shared knowledge is the shortest path to enlightenment...”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hmm.
Not a philosophy that would appeal to my brother...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Is Prince Trion somehow involved...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ah, forgive me. I was merely thinking aloud...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The “Gordeus.”
I have heard this name somewhere before...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What manner of person is this?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Not a person? So, it is a holy relic enshrined in Walahra Temple...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In the distant past, Sage Walahra once unraveled the Gordeus and grasped the fundamental principle of existence...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And now a host of like-minded scholars toil day and night to discover the same loose thread to unravel the Gordeus for themselves.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It appears the people of the Empire search for quite different truths than the ones we seek...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The Walahra Philosophy?
What manner of learning is this?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What connection does this philosophy have to the Astral Candescence?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “From the void all things are born. To the void all things return.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I do not understand what this “void” they speak of refers to.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Though this philosophy is not so far from our own belief that all life begins and ends with Great Altana and the mothercrystals...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ohohoho!
Too much time in the cathedral for Destin's little boy!
The mind is a tool you must sharpen, not a child's toy!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do you mock me, Doctor Shantotto!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You look for your answers in all the wrong places.
Shall I bring a little hope to your long, dreary faces?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What are you hiding, Shantotto?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The servants of Walahra control the Hall of Binding--the treasure's little nest.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The Hall of Binding is defended by the Serpent Generals--the best of the best!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The Serpent Generals?
A name I have heard. Each one is said to be worth a thousand soldiers.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The Astral Candescence is strictly monitored by the Walahra Temple, according to the adventurer's speech...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But the treasure is kept in an area that the beastmen can easily reach.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And there we find the Serpent Generals, the strongest of the strong...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Plus mercenaries like ≺Player Name≻ to help them, if I'm not wrong?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yes, there does seem to be some contradiction to be found here.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You see...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
This is a huge game of “set the trap and wait.”
And the Astral Candescence is the very tasty bait!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Of course!
Why didn't I see it?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
But wait.
This creates a whole new set of questions.
Why would they want the beastmen in the city?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
There are some things that even I cannot divine.
It's time to sit back and wait for a sign.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But it does seem that this problem lies at the center of some grand plan.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Without concern for the people of Al Zahbi...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We need more information.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Yes.
An individual of keen wits and sharp senses...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My lords, I have a suggestion.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Player Name≻ is employed as a mercenary in the Empire.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: However, ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 0)≻[she/he] is a distinguished adventurer, who will not sell ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[his/her] principles for a bag of gil.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I point to the safe delivery of the sage's letter as proof of ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[his/her] dedication.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A long journey without promise of reward.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And I am sure that all of you present have had numerous beneficial dealings with adventurers.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: They have earned our trust and respect!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That is why I put forth the motion that we have ≺Player Name≻ return to the Empire and fight as a mercenary.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We cannot allow any more blood to be spilled by beastmen, even should that blood belong to another nation's people.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And if ≺Player Name≻ can improve ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[his/her] standing enough to bring ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[him/her] closer to the Imperial palace...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We may learn the ultimate goal of the Empire.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You'll find no argument here.
Adventurers have been the quiet heroes in many of Bastok's darker moments.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
An idea that creates less work for us,
will not find me making a needless fuss!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: How does the Duchy of Jeuno stand on this?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In agreement.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The linking of our auction house services has strengthened the ties between Jeuno and the Empire, but economical matters are superseded by politics...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: All in favor...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
One moment.
As Raillefal warned, this problem is not likely to remain constrained within the borders of the Near East.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: All the lands of Vana'diel, including our four nations...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Urhguum” is the word for “world” in the language of Aht Urhgan, and this lurking threat could plunge it entirely into chaos.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We lay this mission before you, ≺Player Name≻.
Will you consent to take up this burden?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Take up the burden?
≺Selection Dialog≻That's what I'm here for!
What am I, a donkey?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You have our thanks, ≺Player Name≻.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Naturally, we will do all in our power to aid you in this task.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is a trifling amount, but perhaps you might use this Aht Urhgan coin on your travels.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An adventurer is free to choose ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[his/her] own path...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
However, what I ask of you is for the sake of all Vana'diel.
I am sure that when the time comes, I can rely on you to perform your duty.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That treasure is more than simple bait...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An astral relic can and will seal your fate.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The Empress goes too far in her game.
I'm curious to see how it turns out, all the same...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Well met! I'm a Merry Map Marker, and I'd love to make marks all over your merry ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻, but it appears you are missing the markable map I mention.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Good day! I'm a Merry Map Marker, and I'd be emphatically ecstatic if you'd allow me to mark your magical map!≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: A markless ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ is like a motherless maiden, meandering through a miasmatic mire of misery.≺Prompt≻

Embark on a map-marking mission?
≺Selection Dialog≻Mark me up!

field.Element:Text: Here is the area's ≺Set Color #5≻home point≺Set Color #1≻. Once set, your muted remains will be moved here if you are ever...mortally mangled in the midst of a melee.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: And mayhap you are immeasurably motivated to compete in the medieval mayhem of Conflict? Might I suggest you mingle with the modest ≺Set Color #5≻Pursuivant≺Set Color #1≻ located here?≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Ah, and in the case you might wish to mask a meritorious moniker and replace it with one a mite more merited, a ≺Set Color #5≻traveling bard≺Set Color #1≻ strums upon his mellifluous harp here.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Here, you may meet with a member of the Specialty Goods Trade Union. And, if you are a citizen of this mighty dominion, he'll ≺Set Color #5≻teleport≺Set Color #1≻ you all across Vana'diel (for a menial amount of monetary remuneration).≺Prompt≻

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Those men and women wondering how their deeds are mirrored in the minds of the locals should meander over to this gossip-meister to muster up important material on their respective ≺Set Color #5≻reputations≺Set Color #1≻.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: And here is the ≺Set Color #5≻item depository≺Set Color #1≻ where you may store much of your festive furniture, etcetera until misplaced holiday merriment makes it way back into your miserly heart.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Let me begin with Southern San d'Oria.≺Prompt≻

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I shall start with Port Bastok and its magnificent drawbridge.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Now let me move on to the mercantile metropolis known as the Bastok Markets.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And after the markets, come the massive Bastok Mines.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And finally, who could forget the marveled Bastok Metalworks, where masterful minds from across the Republic meet to mull over the mysteries of man-made mechanical marvels.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Let me start with the Windurst Waters.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Let me continue by marking your map of Windurst Walls.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And while I am at it, let me see your map of Heavens Tower.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I shall begin by marking the important locations on your map of the Ru'Lude Gardens.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Next, let me mark your map of Upper Jeuno. Did you know that I often frequent the Marble Bridge whenever I have a free moment? There's just something about the name of that model establishment...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Now let me mark your map of Lower Jeuno.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And finally, I shall mark your map of Port Jeuno.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: ≺Player Name≻!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
<Huff>...You're about to enter the council?
Glad to see you made it in time.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Right, then! This way to the meeting room!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But before you go in, why don't you take a few moments to gather your thoughts?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I mean, they've been going at this for hours--I doubt they'll miss you a couple minutes more.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 34) 1≻≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: As I've already stated numerous times, it is in our best interests to prevent the completion of the Empire's secret weapon, this “iron colossus” of theirs.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Bastok is prepared to employ military action to accomplish this goal--without your support, if necessary.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I am in full agreement with the captain in this case.
The Empire's intentions are clear--we must not lose this race.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But if we mobilize our forces, we will be giving the Grand Vizier and his supporters just the ammunition they need to fuel a full-scale war.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The Empress yet retains loyal subjects within Her realm. I believe we can still avoid open confrontation.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ohohoho...so unlike you, my dear prince.
Your sentimental view of the situation is making me wince.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If I'm not mistaken, Your Highness, wasn't it one of your agents that described the Empress's position as little more than a puppet on the throne?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This will be a conflict of epic proportions. Perhaps we should strive harder for a diplomatic solution...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: While I agree with you in theory, we walk a dangerous line.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Despite its state of constant warfare, the sprawling Empire commands staggering resources. If we fail to make the first move, we could face casualties on the scale of the Great War.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The Great War? Surely you jest?
The carnage from this apocalypse will be far greater than all the rest.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Worse than the Great War?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You all know of the Gordeus, I presume?
It is best we're all aware of this potential source of doom.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: One does not lightly forget such an object...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You speak of the sacred artifact kept within the Walahra Temple?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An amazing creation worthy of mention.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But that is not the phenomenon to which I wish to draw your attention.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I refer to an event from nine hundred years before...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The supernova that was born from the earth and stole the night sky for an entire year, as was passed down in lore.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ah, now this I recall from my lessons!
This was the miracle bestowed by the Goddess that marked the beginning of the Crystal Era.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: After the glare finally faded, this star of the first magnitude became part of the Alexander constellation, correct?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
It was merely a coincidence that the supernova's trajectory passed in front of that star.
The truth of the matter is more fascinating by far.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The trajectory? I don't understand.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I discovered an ancient papyrus in the extensive vaults of the Optistery.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The following was written in a script bold and flowery:≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “When the light deity clashed with the dark, rent in twain were the heavens, and devastated was the earth by a storm beyond comprehension.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I must admit to feeling a degree of shock,
for this simple passage described the arrival of Ragnarok...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ragnarok...
The northern legend that tells of the twilight of the gods?
You mean to tell us that this supernova was in fact the aftermath of a battle between divinities?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Oh, so close to the mark.
Shall I endeavor to bring you out of the dark?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This is my hypothesis based on the facts at hand...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The old Empire of Aht Urhgan launched their iron colossus, imbued with the spirit of the light deity, high into the air, and attempted to dominate the entire land.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The nation that revered a rival deity was unsurprisingly not amused.
They sent up their Dark Rider born from sacrifice and with utter darkness infused.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A fierce battle raged in the skies, and eventually both combatants fell to earth--the giant in pieces, and the rider with grave wounds to his material form.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But this titanic struggle had blasted the land into ruin, and left a void in the heavens that spawned a cataclysmic storm...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An apocalypse...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What a ridiculous story.
How could an iron colossus be made to fly?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And what does this have to do with the name of the Gordeus?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We Tarutaru have always been notoriously fussy about our cuisine.
The name was probably heard from a trader in foreign goods, is what I mean.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The name of the colossus's heart, given to a star...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We have let ourselves be distracted by the candescences. The Gordeus should have been our true concern.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We can only hope that the Grand Vizier has failed to notice the true value of the treasure under his nose.
We must hurry to bring this matter to a close.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Naji reporting in!
I've brought ≺Player Name≻ back with me!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You're late. Where in Altana's name have you been!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Take it easy, Ayame.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻, we are grateful you could come.
Your insight will be invaluable.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Please, describe to us your impressions of the events unfolding in the Empire...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thanks to your talents, gaining the program data we needed was far less complicated than expected.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But the Empress appears to have only a tentative hold on consciousness...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is nothing to be concerned about. When reading someone's memories with my altered...perspective...it occasionally releases images and thoughts sealed deep within the mind.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
This state of regression is only temporary.
She will recover in time...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Let us begin.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So...this day has finally come.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That voice!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If it isn't Nashmeira, then who...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I know not who you are, but it appears you have completed construction of Alzadaal and unraveled the Gordeus.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Congratulations are in order!
You will soon hold the most awe-inspiring weapon in Urhguum in the palm of your hand--the power of light.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Father...!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But the power of Alexander is a double-edged sword.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Mother!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The infinite energy of a star...
The legends--not to mention the ruins--speak eloquently of the destruction that will befall should you make a single misstep.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:
You've recovered one of the long-lost mog tablets!
You should share the news of your discovery with the Explorer Moogle in Ru'Lude Gardens.≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Greetings, adventurer!
You've heard the tale of the mog tablets, haven't you?
If any of them turn up in your travels, promise you'll let me know, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 0)≻[Greetings/Happy Vana'versary], my adventuring friend!
Thanks to your efforts, the mog tablets have been recovered, and their magic freed to spread happiness and joy across the realm!
You are truly a friend to all mooglekind, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Oh no! What a shame, kupo!
The mog tablets that were recovered have been scattered to the ends of Vana'diel once more...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ask about something?
≺Selection Dialog≻What's a mog tablet?
The history of mog tablets.
List of tablets.
Nothing.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ask about something?
≺Selection Dialog≻What's a mog tablet?
The history of mog tablets.
Collected tablets.
The current Super Kupower.
Nothing.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ask about something?
≺Selection Dialog≻What's a mog tablet?
The history of mog tablets.
Nothing.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What's a mog tablet!? What's a mog tablet, you say!?
Why, only the most awesome, amazing artifact in the annals of moogle history, that's what, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There's eleven of them in all, to be exact, scattered to the far reaches of Vana'diel and just waiting to be discovered by brave adventurers like you!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What happens if you find them? I thought you'd never ask, kupo!
Each tablet is inscribed with an ancient moogle poem of joy, and legend has it that if all are found, the ancient moogle magic of King Kupofried the Great will be released once more, spreading joy and happiness through all the land!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We explorer moogles have made it our life's work to recover the tablets and unlock their powers.
But with these short legs and little-bitty wings, we can't do it alone, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
There! I've whipped up a spell that will instantly transport any tablets you find back here to me.
Come back if you find anything, and happy exploring, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Just sit right back and I'll tell you the tale, kupo.
Many, many ages past, we moogles had our own glorious kingdom.
It was truly the peak of moogle civilization, a veritable golden age for all mooglekind!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The seventh king of this great nation was the wise and kindly King Kupofried, a masterful magician famed as the father of the fantastic moogle magic that survives to this very day, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
In his later years, King Kupofried embarked on what would become the greatest work of his illustrious reign.
Seeking to pass down the prosperity of his kingdom to future generations, he inscribed eleven incantations of moogle joy and happiness onto eleven stone tablets.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Sadly, the kindly king's intentions went unappreciated by his selfish sons and daughters, and many a fierce feud broke out over who would inherit these relics, kupo...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
King Kupofried was greatly dismayed.
How could the poems that he had composed out of pure love and joy become the root of such strife?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In his despair, the king commanded his minion bats to scatter the tablets to the far corners of the world, where they would be seen by moogle eyes no more.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Alas! I only wanted my children to be happy, kupo,” he lamented, and flew away on his tiny yet majestic wings, never to be seen in his kingdom again.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Left without its wise monarch, the once-glorious moogle kingdom fractured into warring tribes, falling into unrest...and, eventually, ruin.
A tragic tale, don't you think, kupo?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We explorer moogles are the proud descendants of King Kupofried, living only to bring our last great monarch's unrealized dream to fruition.
We will--we must!--find the mog tablets and bring true joy and happiness to this world!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Let's see...
It appears that ≺Numeric Parameter 0≻ moogle ≺Singular/Plural Choice (Parameter 0)≻[tablet has/tablets have] already been found, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Here's a list of all the located tablets, kupo!≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
Oh, glorious day!
All eleven mog tablets have been recovered and restored to their rightful place at the altar of King Kupofried!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Can you feel the ancient moogle magic in the air?
You can now bask in the benefits of this Super Kupower...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Thrifty Transit”!
A special treat for the cost-conscious adventurer!
For a limited time, all survival guide costs are eliminated, and you are able to teleport between nearby cities for a small fee, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Martial Master”!
As an added bonus to your Signet, combat skills will increase more rapidly! Your magic and automaton skills will be boosted, too!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Blood of the Vampyr”!
Signets have been boosted with the abilities of Regeneration and Refresh!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Treasure Hound”!
With Signet in effect, you will now be able to sniff out more treasure and gil! Great riches surely await you, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Artisan's Advantage”!
Good news for aspiring artisans, kupo! When receiving advanced image support, the chance of your ingredients being lost in a failed synthesis attempt has been drastically reduced!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Myriad Mystery Boxes”!
What's this, kupo? Mysterious boxes have been sighted all over the realm!
What genius could have devised such commendable creations?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Dilatory Digestion”!
Not content to be left behind, brown magic slides back out for another go, kupo!
Now you can be what you eat for twice as long and save on all those trips to your local merchant.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Boundary Buster”!
Trust in Signet and you can never go wrong, kupo!
It's time to take to the field and vanquish a veritable army of enemies, for any Conquest Points you receive will be duly doubled!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Bountiful Bazaar”!
Trade routes are bustling with unprecedented traffic and peddlers' carts are overflowing with objects now that regional goods are available to merchants across the realm, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Swift Shoes”!
This is just the ticket for today's busy adventurer! For a limited time, provided that you're fully rested and healed, your legs will carry you with the speed of a chocobo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Crystal Caboodle”!
Signet is now better than ever! Collect crystals from beastmen-controlled areas...and maybe even clusters from other areas!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Be warned that our moogle magic is concentrated around this altar.
If you venture to far-off lands, the Super Kupowers will be unable to protect you...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What? What about the past, you say?
Of course the magic won't travel through time.
What a strange question, kupo...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But not an altogether pointless, one. The powers of thirtfy transit do seem to apply across the space-time continuum, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The whole system is filled with mysteries.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Oh, it's you! It's really you!
The brave adventurer who discovered one of our mog tablets!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
It's a pleasure, an honor to meet you, kupo!
We have a special prize to reward you for your efforts.
If you'll just sign right here...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

≺Selection Dialog≻Sure.
I don't think so.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
Oh, thank you, ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Mister/Miss]...≺Player Name≻!
A truly heroic name, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
As a reward for your efforts, please have this!
Many thanks, and ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 0)≻[safe travels/Happy Vana'versary], kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What? You won't? That's a shame, kupo.
I had a special prize here just for you, but without your signature, I'll just have to hold on to it...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
If you change your mind, come back quickly.
The mog tablets will be scattered to the wind again at any moment, kupo...≺Prompt≻
