field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻.
What brings you to the Duchy wearing such a grave expression?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...I see.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Needless to say, it is beyond my station to render a decision on affairs of state.
Wait here. I will consult with my superiors.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is as I expected. The Duchy will hold formal deliberations as to the potential repercussions of our involvement in this matter.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Chin up, ≺Player Name≻. The earnestness of the Empire's plea has not been lost on our diplomats.
Perhaps the “Silent Empire” truly intends to change its ways...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I can offer no promises, but encourage you to do what you can in the meantime.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You make for the three nations from here, do you not?
Then be on your way, and have faith that good tidings will await you upon your return.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Have you received consent from the three nations?
Not yet, you say? Then I suggest you get moving.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The seals of the three nations...yes, everything seems to be in order.
Good work.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You'll be pleased to know that the Duchy has also agreed to give its consent.
Here are the relevant papers.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I trust you'll see that this matter ends well for all of us, ≺Player Name≻.
Now you'd best be on your way.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You there. Yes, you, adventurer! Your downcast countenance tells me your life wants for exhilaration.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Who am I, you ask? Let's just say I'm he who is about to banish all trace of tedium from your life with an irresistible offer--one of otherworldly proportions, to be sure. For a mere ≺Numeric Parameter 1≻ gil, this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ I hold is yours.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“But what in Slumbering Samwell's shank does it do,” you ask?
Consider yourself fortunate, for it's my policy to demystify before the customer buys.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What will you do?
≺Selection Dialog≻Let him ramble.
Purchase ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻6≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻.
Learn how to use it.
Discard abyssite.
Leave.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ahem! Allow me to present you with a supposition.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Lying in parallel to the world upon which we stand exists another dimension.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Abyssea” is its name--or at least, the name I've bestowed upon it.
It is a world of boundless beauty, mystique, and riches unclaimed.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Now, suppose this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ I hold is a key to accessing Abyssea.
Were you in possession of one, your curiosity would get the better of you, yes?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Strictly speaking, this object does not grant entry into Abyssea itself.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It does, however, make it possible to interact with beings from that plane of existence--“Abysseans,” I call them.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ serves to detect Abysseans that wander the gulf between worlds.
How those hapless creatures--I refer to them as “Voidwalkers”--found their way there, mind you, is another subject entirely.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Having drifted to this realm from the world yonder, much like the Voidwalkers themselves, ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻5≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ are attuned to the presence of these creatures and will react--vibrate and emit light--when they draw near.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The closer your distance to a Voidwalker, the stronger the reaction becomes, until the creature is forcibly wrested into this dimension.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Repeated contact with Abysseans will cause the ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ to take on different hues, allowing it to respond to creatures belonging to the higher echelons of Voidwalkers.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Be forewarned! Abysseans are among the most foul-tempered, unpredictable creatures.
You would do well to steel yourself for a trying encounter prior to making contact.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I trust your many adventures have made you familiar with those ghastly statues scattered across the land called cavernous maws.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My observations have revealed that the concentration of Voidwalkers is greatest in locations where these statues are found.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: As yet, I have no plausible explanations for this phenomenon, but you needn't concern yourself with such details.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yours, my friend, is a dilemma infinitely simpler in nature.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: All this far-fetched talk of Abyssea, Abysseans, and Voidwalkers...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'm fully aware of the fantastical nature of my tale, and do not think poorly of those inclined to skepticism.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Yet I feel no need to vouch further for the authenticity of my claims.
Such is my confidence that the truth speaks for itself.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Now then. A great new world has presented itself before you.
The question is, will you embrace this opportunity, or let it pass you by?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
As Abysseans cross from one realm to another, so too does gil pass from one individual to the next.
In my mind, it is only fitting that gil is that which grants you the key to Abyssea.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
My tales have piqued your interest, have they?
As I have mentioned prior, the price is ≺Numeric Parameter 0≻ gil.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hand over ≺Numeric Parameter 0≻ gil?
≺Selection Dialog≻Aye.
Nay.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
No? The sum I ask is by no means prohibitive.
I'll be waiting here, should you ever change your mind.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I thank you for your custom.
Here is your very own ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: As a service for all customers, upon request I will take your ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ off your hands and dispose of it in your stead.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The ability to meddle with inter-dimensional matter can be considered a great power, with which comes great responsibility.
Indeed there have been those who found the burden beyond their capacity to cope.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It seems you are short on gil. Yet I cannot grant concessions, lest access to otherworldly realms lose its true value.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I see you've developed a taste for ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻5≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻. Yet I fear I cannot furnish you further, for one alone is sufficient to invite misfortune upon the heedless.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You wish to know how to use the ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻?
There is no trick to it. Allow me to demonstrate.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
While in possession of ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻6≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻, simply assume a resting pose.
I'm given to understand it is second nature to all adventurers.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Doing so will cause your ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ to react. Pertinent information can be gleaned by observing the magnitude of its vibration and the manner of light emitted.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Should neither reaction occur, take it to mean that no Voidwalkers roam the area.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Should it vibrate softly but emit no light, take it to mean that Voidwalkers have recently passed through and may soon return.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Should it vibrate softly and emit a gentle light, take it to mean that Voidwalkers presently roam the area.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Now, pay particular attention to what I'm about to explain.
The reaction of the ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ will change once a predetermined distance from a Voidwalker has been closed.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
From that point onwards, the magnitude of the vibration corresponds directly to the creature's strength.
Based on this knowledge, it is your decision whether to pursue it further.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The gentle glow of light, on the other hand, will intensify to become a radiant beam pointing in the direction of the creature.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Following that beam to its end will cause the heretofore invisible Voidwalker to cross fully over into this world and take form.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This precise moment of encounter with an Abyssean, I have dubbed “contact.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Not only are Abysseans known to be temperamental and unpredictable; there are those that demonstrate a degree of cunning and guile far beyond that seen in this world.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Consider yourself warned.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: For as surely as the beam of light emitted by the ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ guides you to a Voidwalker, so too does it guide the Voidwalker to you. Be ever mindful of this fact.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Know also that not one, but numerous Voidwalkers may roam the land at any given time, and the readings indicate only the creature nearest you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You would do well to check the readings regularly, as a sudden change in the light's direction could mean a different Voidwalker has wandered your way.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Voidwalkers will only reveal their true form at the point of contact, and seeking one only to be met with another is a scenario all adventurers want to avoid.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
But surely, you grow weary of my ramblings.
I for one believe this is something best learned through doing.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Has the burden of this responsibility proven too heavy to bear?
Very well, I will take it off your hands and see to its disposal.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Discard which one?
≺Selection Dialog≻≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 80) 1≻≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻

None of them.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Are you certain?
≺Selection Dialog≻Aye.
Nay.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
It is done. You needn't concern yourself with unseen foes any longer.
A tame, tranquil adventuring life bereft of exhilaration will be yours once more.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Forgive me. My personal thirst for the unknown has no bearing on the decisions of others.
I will be here, however, should you have a change of heart.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
≺Numeric Parameter 0≻ gil paid.
Obtained key item: ≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 80) 1≻≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3ａ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻!≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
Kupo-ho! Another adventurer has found ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[his/her] way to my domain.
Was it my aura of superior sagacity that led you here? This conspicuous crate and chest that sit seductively at my side?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Many secrets have I to tell, but sadly, they would be beyond your meager mental faculties to fathom.
Return when your abilities are up to the task.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
It is no matter.
What matters is that you are here, and from the look of it, you are a suitable subject for the task I would entrust to you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I speak to you on behalf of the Magian Mooglehood, an ancient and august assembly of wisemoogles hailing from the once-glorious Kingdom of Kupalika.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Our predecessors were councilors and confidants to none other than the celebrated King Kupofried himself.
To this day, it is our mission to safeguard the secrets of their moogle magic and see them properly passed down to posterity.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Each illustrious member of the Magian Mooglehood guards knowledge of a distinct branch of our lineal lore.
My specialty lies in weaponry; with my aid, you will be doling out damage and destruction in ways heretofore unimagined!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “What impelled you to impart this long-withheld wisdom to us? And why now, kupo?” the unenlightened adventurer might ask.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: To which the wise moogle would readily reply: The answer, my friend, is in the mog tablets--those remarkable relics wrought by King Kupofried himself--that were only recently recovered by resourceful adventurers such as rrr...yourself.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
There is an ancient (and somewhat alarming) prophecy in our mooglehood.
It goes...<ahem>...“King Kupofried's creations shall slumber soundly until such time as their Super Kupowers are called upon to save the realm from utter ruin, kupo.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The particulars of the prophecy--preposterous as this may seem--outstrip even our prodigious powers of perception.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yet this I know, kupo: if moogle magic is what shall deliver this world from destruction, then moogle magic this world shall have--in abundance!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
As an adventurer of renown, repute, and paramount prowess, you would seem a worthy beneficiary for our boon.
And yet the Magian Mooglehood is nothing if not meticulously methodical. No, we must be certain...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I propose to task you with a series of trials.
Each time you emerge victorious, we shall proffer you a portion of our powers, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What say you, adventurer?
Will you undertake the Trial of the Magians, that you might one day wield the mightiest of moogle magic to save your realm from destruction and devastation?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Tackle the Trial of the Magians, kupo?
≺Selection Dialog≻Will I ever!
Maybe another time...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Excellent.
Then my first gift unto you shall be this: a journal that shall serve to record all of your extraordinary exploits.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We understand, for with great kupower comes great responsibility.
Should you ever be willing to bear the burden, we shall welcome your return.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You, who would inherit the mysteries of the magians...speak unto me your wish, kupo.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
Welcome to the MHMU's porter service, kupo!
Which of your burdensome belongings shall I take off your hands today?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Do something, kupo?
≺Selection Dialog≻Porter service?
Buy a storage slip.
No, thank you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Is your gobbiebag splitting at the seams? Mog Safe spilling over?
Why, an accomplished adventurer like yourself surely has more stuff than you know what to do with.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
That's where I come in, kupo.
I'll gladly hold onto your prized possessions, freeing you space to gather up even grander goodies.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: To make use of my services, first you'll need to buy one of these storage slips for the low, low fee of ≺Numeric Parameter 19≻ gil.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Storage slips come in numerous varieties, kupo, each corresponding to a different type of item.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You'll want to peruse the fine print closely, so you don't end up paying good gil for a scrap of parchment useless for the particular item you wish to store.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Not that we moogles would object to that sort of donation, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Choose the item you wish to entrust, then trade it to me along with a single storage slip.
I will take the item and return the slip to you, marked with an invisible seal.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Invisible to you, at least.
It's plain as day to us moogles, so don't even think of trying to pull one over on us, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: When it comes time to retrieve your item, just trade to me a single storage slip--any slip--once again.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I will present you with a list of all the items currently in my care, and you may choose the one you wish to withdraw.
Simple as that, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What's more, no additional transaction fees will be incurred!
Pretty generous of us for a change, no?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Now I bet you're wondering what the catch is, kupo.
So as not to disappoint you, there are a few!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: For one, any signed items will lose their signatures if you store them with me.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Why, you say? Hey, even we moogles aren't perfect!
It's better for both of us if you keep your most precious possessions close at hand, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Now listen up, because there's another catch, and it's a doozy.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
If you lose your storage slip, I won't be able to return your item. Ever. No ifs, ands, or buts!
No “I'm sorry, Mister Porter Moogle, it'll never happen again!”
Rules are rules, kupo, and someone has to keep them.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Last, but not least, I can't accept equipment bearing Magian trial insignia.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If you have such an item that you're simply dying to entrust to me, you'll have to abandon your trial first, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
And that's all there is to it.
This humble moogle can hardly wait to serve you!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I hear you have proven yourself capable on the field.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
The Voidwalker threat grows ever more grave by the day.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Were the Duchy to fall to this extradimensional menace, it would spell disaster for the realm.
This should be evident to even a grunt such as yourself.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In the name of His Excellency Kam'lanaut, Archduke of Jeuno, I hereby authorize you for participation in all Voidwatch operations conducted under the Duchy's jurisdiction.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do not forget to report back to an officer upon completing an objective, lest your accomplishments go overlooked.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I remind you again...≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Do your best not to join them.

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻! I've received word of your accomplishments in Qufim.

field.Element:Text:
≺Player Name≻! I've received word of your accomplishments.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Yes, we must discover a means to seal the rifts once and for all.
Then, and only then, will victory truly be ours.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Until that day, we have no choice but to continue the fight.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: They say such stores of power exist inside us all, yet most will train a lifetime without ever learnin' how to tap into 'em...≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
But let's get to the heart of the mattaru, ≺Player Name≻.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Listen, and listen well.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Using the energies within you, I've burned into your soul the ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻.

field.Element:Text:

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Before that, though, I really could use a good meal and a...<yawn>...nap.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: A man in demand? More like a lazy louse, kupo.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
As enigmatic as our friend is, the realm may never know.
Heh heh...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Let up not in your training, ≺Player Name≻. The path to true martial mastery lies before you.

field.Element:Text: You learned the secret technique of the bushin!≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text: Our research team has confirmed the presence of new rifts in the greater three nations area.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Under normal circumstances, the defense effort would fall under the jurisdiction of the local governments.
This time, however, I fear the circumstances are far from normal.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

We're counting on you, ≺Player Name≻.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

field.Element:Text: Ducal researchers have alerted us to the presence of newly formed planar rifts in the vicinity of the three kingdoms.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:

We fear that this time, however, their limited resources and manpower will do little to stem the tide of this formidable enemy.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hence, we turn to you.

field.Element:Text: As we trust you are already aware...≺Prompt≻

Direct supervision of the Voidwatch operation will be conducted by our officers dispatched to the three nations.

field.Element:Text: ≺Player Name≻. Once again you prove that the Duchy's faith in you was not misplaced.≺Prompt≻

You are an asset to the Voidwatch.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Until we can identify and eliminate the source of the threat, we have no recourse but to call upon you again.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
In the meantime, take this as recompense for your efforts.

field.Element:Text: Hmph. Two, you say?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Aye. One buried in the sands of the Valkurm Dunes, the other on Buburimu Peninsula.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Your Excellency...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
This adventurer is a veteran Voidwatcher.
I would have ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[him/her] hear your findings as well.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
At present, it responds to neither ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ nor ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3ａ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻.
We are unable to gauge the potential danger of any Voidwalkers that may lie beyond.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Intriguing.
So the portal between dimensions is not yet fully formed...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
It is only a matter of time before the monsters spring forth.
Let up your watch not for a second, and send word the moment you detect anything amiss.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Sir! Yes, sir!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It would seem your next mission will begin sooner rather than later, soldier.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
We will authorize you for participation at such time as it is necessary.
In the meantime, I suggest you rest up and prepare yourself for the challenges ahead.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Too much remains unknown about these rifts.
I grow impatient with our researchers and their incessant pleas for more time.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I concur. The situation threatens to spiral out of control.

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Player Name≻ has proved a most useful...resource...in the pursuit of our goals.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
And yet there are limits to what one adventurer--or even an army of them--can do.
It seems that we have no choice but to get involved more...directly.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...Yes, Your Excellency.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
The Archduke will be pleased.

field.Element:Text: The data we have recovered from your latest mission is...not promising.≺Prompt≻

Stay alive, and do not stray too far.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text:
I am sure you understand why we have summoned you on such short notice.
Yes, it does indeed concern the Voidwalkers.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Recently, however, some new facts have come to light. Reports confirm a new substance that can be culled from those planes-walking fiends.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is said to possess two separate forms: one is that of a crystal, the other of a more granular structure resembling cruor. Its alabaster hue, however, serves to distinguish it from that vermilion currency.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: While it may exhibit crystalline properties, it is unlike any specimen of crystal we have heretofore examined. The oft-used phrase “shrouded in mystery” does not begin to describe how it baffles even our most accomplished researchers.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We may have nothing more to guide us than conjecture, but we cannot discard the possibility that this mineral is an integral piece in the calamitous puzzle that Vana'diel faces. Do not hesitate to collect as large a sample as possible of this mysterious mineral.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Should you require further intelligence, seek out a Voidwatch Officer. As they are the ones who operate in the field, they should be privy to the most current of information.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Furthermore...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Whether as hardened stone or dust deposits, this substance is less than abundant.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Voidwatch Officers should be willing to part with some samples, however, should you fail to harvest any off of Voidwalker corpses.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: No matter the method by which you obtain it, this mineral should shine new light on this catastrophe and allow you to more efficiently aid our cause.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: To the extent of our knowledge, there is no new planar rift activity, but you of all people should understand the spontaneous nature of these interdimensional disturbances. None of us can let our guard down for even a moment.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Archduke Kam'lanaut expects great things of you as well.
It is quite regrettable that he could not honor us with his presence today, but he is a busy man with many entice--er, engagements.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Now that you understand how you can be of service, it is time you got to your duties. Let us conclude this parley.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: But where are my manners? I have not yet introduced myself. I am Anastase, an emissary sent from the Sacred City of Adoulin.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I see. I must admit to feeling a twinge of disappointment, but I understand.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: My stay here will be a long one, so if you have a change of heart, please come and see me again.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Have you changed your mind? Will you help me study the geomagnetic founts?≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I come from the Sacred City of Adoulin, an island that lies far to the west, beyond the great Sea of Zafmlug.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Further still beyond the island is the continent of Ulbuka, where a pristine expanse of nature sits unsullied by mortal hands.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Tales of men and women from the Middle Lands who cannot resist the clarion call of a good deed left undone have stretched across the sea and reached my ears. Hearing these tales prompted me to make the arduous journey here.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: For you see, I desire your assistance in our quest to pioneer the undeveloped lands of Ulbuka.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I had hoped to secure transport in advance for those interested in cooperating with this enterprise.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: But executing a plan is never a simple affair. Air and sea vessels are indeed available, but unsustainable in the long term due to the staggering distance between the two continents.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Yet one possibility exists. In our beloved city, devices called “waypoints” allow the user to instantaneously move from one location to another.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: However, I am not certain whether the ley lines to which these waypoints are attuned traverse the oceans to the Middle Lands. My first task, therefore, is to find locations suitable for such travel.≺Prompt≻

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What I ask is that you use ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻6≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ to...oh?≺Prompt≻

field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ is ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻6ａ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ for the Middle Lands.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: What I would ask of you is that you attune the ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ to the aforementioned geomagnetic founts.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If this survey is successful, then it will surely guarantee a prosperous trading partnership for our two homelands.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I shall be waiting here to collect your ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ when you have completed this endeavor.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Many years have I spent researching and analyzing these phenomena. Sensing any changes in the object I have given you is merely a trifle.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: To a layman's eyes, though, any deviations are impossible to detect.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My hope is that, should these portals become fully active, even the uninitiated will be able to make such determinations with ease.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I am sure you have noticed this mysterious device resting at my side. In Adoulin, we refer to items of its ilk as “waypoints.”≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: These portals enable instantaneous transportation between two locations simply by holding up ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻6≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ to them.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Ah yes, before I forget--other members of my expedition have already gone to survey these locations.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: You have traveled to the ≺Numeric Parameter 0≻ locations I have requested and recorded the data in the geomagnetic founts there!≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Among their ranks are geomancers and rune fencers--a rare sight in the Middle Lands, to be sure.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If you were to visit Adoulin, you may be able to find out about their secrets for yourself.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Forgive my loose tongue. Some things should be found out for oneself.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: My efforts now are focused on obtaining information about any more geomagnetic founts that may exist. I may have more information for you at a later date.≺Prompt≻

Thanks, but no thanks.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: I sense the hands of fate have bound us together through our mutually insatiable curiosity.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And yes, my intrepid friend, Quwi Orihbhe has found yet more locations for us...well, you...to examine.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Would you like to hear more?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Which prediction would you like to hear?
≺Selection Dialog≻None.
How do I record the areas?
<Abandoned Village>.≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 16)≻[ /: Complete]
<Malediction>.≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 17)≻[ /: Complete]
<Faeries>.≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 18)≻[ /: Complete]

<Belfry>.≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 24)≻[ /: Complete]
<Darkness>.≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 25)≻[ /: Complete]≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hmm... What can I give you to go on?
“≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 0)≻[A church standing in an abandoned village/Beyond a hall wrapped in curses/An abode of faeries worshipping a living god/A city swallowed by the land/An eroded cave where space twists and turns/A temple where those who have lost darkness reside/Moss that glistens deep within a gigantic tree/A city constructed by nomadic beastmen/Another beautiful ring of a bell/The farthest reaches of the blackest depths].”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Would that I could tell you more, but as previously, I can only relay what was told to me.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Just as you have overcome past trials and tribulations, so too shall you triumph this day.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I believe in you!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: May your steps be swift and your blades true.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: As you most likely have presumed, Quwi Orhibhe has...oh?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
...!
The founts are...already recorded!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What...what sorcery is this?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do you have feelers throughout the far reaches of the land? Or...are you a wizard?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My feeble mind cannot comprehend how you have already found the geomagnetic founts that have only just now been divined. H-how...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I do not know by what means you have obtained such information, but I sense that it was some extra-dimensional force...where information is contained for all to see.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I am pleased that you have returned safely. May I see your ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Your efforts have taken you to lands both far and wide. I congratulate you on having trekked so far throughout Vana'diel.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There are no words to describe how I feel for all you have done. Even my most compelling reward is an insufficient prize.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Have you gotten used to using our warp technology? Is it to your liking?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The theoretical magical calculations behind these waypoints are based on, if my records are correct, studies done here in the Middle Lands.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I was but a fledgling researcher at that time, so I am a tad hazy on the details of it all, but my journey from Adoulin has more meaning in light of that fact.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What would you like to know?
≺Selection Dialog≻What about these waypoints?
I need more information.
 
Can I give you a hand with...you know?
Thank you, and good day.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hmm? Whatever do you mean?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I suppose I shouldn't hide behind blank stares...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: For you see, warping to incredibly dangerous locales is, at times, truly frightening. Though I am aware you chose this option out of curiosity...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Knowing what I have just told you, would you still like to accept this task?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Accept his task?
≺Selection Dialog≻It couldn't hurt...much.
On second thought...
Tell me more.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A dead adventurer is of no use to anyone. I cannot fault you for choosing the better part of valor.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What I am about to tell you has never before occurred in Adoulin, so I admit to being at a bit of a loss.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Parties representing, er, former patrons of these waypoints have reported certain...anomalies. Specifically, they occasionally fall down from the heavens. Splat.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My confidantes have been working tirelessly to determine the root cause, and our working theory is that over time, the recorded information becomes weak and unstable.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I would ask that you take this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ and warp to the problematic locales.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Once there, you can confirm the integrity of the spot and correct the recorded information as necessary.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This all sounds more complicated than it really is. All you must do is re-attune the stone to the geomagnetic fount.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: As you have likely gathered, the instability means that I cannot guarantee that you will arrive at your intended destination.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You could end up facing monsters tooth and claw, or be surrounded by an impenetrable mist that seeps into your very soul.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Quite fraught with peril, indeed.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yet if anyone could accomplish this task, it would be you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Y-you mean it? I had just been bluffing, but you're really going to...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Are you absolutely sure?
≺Selection Dialog≻Adventure awaits!
You couldn't pay me enough.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An adventurer you are, in the literal sense of the word!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Let me respond to your courageous request with the utmost confidence!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I hereby present you with this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻. Take it with you to areas for which the recorded data has begun to deteriorate.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There are several locations in question. Which will you choose?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Just how tough do you want this to be?
≺Selection Dialog≻On second thought...
Tough as butter.
Tough as nails.
Tough as diamond.
I require further explanation.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So be it then. I have prepared the waypoint for your use.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: May you come back in one piece!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Back for more? Very well. Pick your poison.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That twinkle in your eye... Is that success I sense?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Your ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻, please!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Yes, the data for the geomagnetic fount has been recorded properly.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: From recording to fixing...is there nothing that adventurers cannot do? Here, a token of my esteem.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Well, would you look...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I am quite pleased to see that you have returned whole.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do not be worried. Though you may not have succeeded this time, the important thing is the waypoints did not spell out your demise.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is my understanding, ≺Player Name≻, that you deign to serve as a pioneer in Adoulin.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Oh yes, not only do I have ears everywhere, but I can see that glowing ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ you hold in your very hands.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My granddaughter guides those new to Adoulin, instructing them in the mysteries of waypoints. Please, give her my regards if you meet her by happenstance.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: She is a sweet girl, very refined, thanks largely to her strict upbringing. I am sure that she will provide you with any assistance you should require.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Why, ≺Player Name≻! What a most pleasant surprise. How can I help you this fine...
What's this? A present from my beloved Alienor?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What a thoughtful young lady she has grown up to be, making me such a delectable treat.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
You wish to know more about how our research is going?
Well, to be frank...I have not received word from ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 1)≻[Jillia/Zurko-Bazurko/Quwi Orihbhe/Wistful Bison] of late.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I hesitate to ask this of you, since I am certain you have other pressing matters to attend to, but would you deliver some of this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ to ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 1)≻[Selbina/Mhaura/Rabao/Norg] for me?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The enchanting smell of brine upon the wind... A tantalizing dish from a devoted granddaughter... What more is there to life?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There is always a snag somewhere with complicated operations such as the one we are engaged in here. This time, I have not received word from ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 1)≻[Jillia/Zurko-Bazurko/Quwi Orihbhe/Wistful Bison].≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thank you for checking up on ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 1)≻[Jillia/Zurko-Bazurko/Quwi Orihbhe/Wistful Bison]. I am relieved to hear that all is well.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Please tell Alienor that I am grateful for her gift and that the people here in Jeuno are treating me with the utmost kindness.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: What manner of farce is this?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An uncouth Tarutaru claiming to be an esteemed guest of Lady Esha'ntarl is running amok demanding the Trust initiative scroll.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My stomach churns each time this ruffian brings up the lady's honorable name. Filth and lies!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ah! There she is!
That dastardly Tarutaru!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Uh-oh!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The scroll! To think she got her grubby hands on it...!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I cannot comprehend the depth of her audacity to steal from the Auroral Palace!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I beseech you, adventurer--smash her like a pane of glass!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Don't just flop around there! Help meee!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Esha'ntarl said I could have it!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The world never appreciates the endless comedic antics of the Chebukki Show!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There's no way I'd ever hit it big, so instead, I decided I'd save the world with the scroll...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'm thinking of starting a troupe called “The Buxom Bosom Buddies”--with me as the chest--err, headliner!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Of course, I can't do it alone. I'll have to get Ulmia, and Esha'ntarl, and that lovely Mumor...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Of course, I can't do it alone. I'll have to get Ulmia, and Esha'ntarl, and...well, I suppose you're pretty satisfactory, too.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And when it comes to the grand finale, we'll need something flashy. Something that only two of me can do.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So that's where my alter ego comes in!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Wh-why are you waiting? Scrape that villainous scum from Vana'diel this minute!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Smash her to bits?
≺Selection Dialog≻Let me get my hammer.
I want to see how this plays out.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
A snip and a snap and a pile of...maps?
A sneer and a tear, time to warp outta here!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Stop being a fish out of water, and become the ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 0)≻[bosom buddy/fan club president] you always knew you could be!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Remember when that old fuddy-duddy exploited your goodwill and had you gather all manner of trinkets for him? We'll use them as props in our revue!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And I think I know who the most delicious male backup dancers would be!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'm sure Papa will help too!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: He'll be in charge of the big kaboom that accompanies us taking the stage!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Think of it! The ultimate magic, brought to fruition by me and me alone!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So, you see?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Trust time!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What does the ritual require?
≺Selection Dialog≻Bonds of trust.
Bonds of camaraderie.
Bonds of friendship.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Trust. Yes, with trust I will have you under my...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Camaraderie. Yes, a true sign of weakness...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Friendship. Ah yes, how much have I lost so far...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This is ridiculous! We don't have a single one of those!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: <Sigh>≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Then there's only one thing to do!
Me...!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
What comes next?
≺Selection Dialog≻“...te...”!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “...or”?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ☆!!!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A whispering voice floats to your ears from nowhere in particular...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You are to truuuuuust Cherukiki～!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You are to loooooove Cherukiki～!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Cherukiki is your friiiiiiend～!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What's this infernal spell!? Has something happened!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Soldier, to me! This Tarutaru ruffian is at the bottom of it all!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You want an alter ego that can use the ultimate magic, don't you～?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A final fantasy worthy of any adventurer!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: She...she escaped...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The talking rat was scurrying about your pockets while you lay prone, so I advise you to check your belongings.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: By Altana above, my eyes must be failing me. Suddenly there were two of them!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I swear...right before she left...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You find the small scroll Cherukiki was holding crumpled in your bags.≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You cannot shake the feeling that she is pulling a fast one...≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Who came up with this “Trust” magic, anyway? Bah. And what use would you have for it?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hey there, ≺Player Name≻! You're familiar with this “Trust” magic, aren't you?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Are you involved with the initiative?
≺Selection Dialog≻Sure am!
Definitely not!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Is that so?
...Then all the better for me.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
...Then you've already got some alter egos?≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 1≻
The whole idea makes my skin crawl.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And, of course, you're going to say you want me to sacrifice myself so you can have another one, hmm?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Would you like Maat's alter ego?
≺Selection Dialog≻Indubitably.
Eeew.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Oh, praise Altana! I thought for a minute that...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: <Sigh>≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You adventurers are all the same. It wasn't so long ago that you would face your challenges head-on with the strength of pure will, but now it's all “Kupipi this” and “Ulmia that”!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: What'll you do if they decide to go rogue, hmm? You've got to learn how to fend for yourself, too!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If I've told you once, I've told you a thousand times. Limits were made to be broken, and that's something only you can do!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So what am I going to do with this scroll I have? Burn it and use the ashes as fertilizer!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Maat! Maat! I come bearing tidings of trouble!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Wh-what is it!? Is Jeuno under attack!?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Oh, dear, the air is filled with angst, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
It's your wife! She..she...≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 1≻
She's waltzing down the warpath!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You left the laundry to languish, forgot to fix the floor, and instead are traipsing about town!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That doesn't sound right. The floor is sparkling like glass in the morning sun, and I remember folding her unmentionables got me thinking of the time when...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: No no no! Those Asuran Fists of yours pounded her panties with such preposterous puissance that they perished in a plume of particles which are presently piling up around your pad!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And that troublesome technique you try on travelers...“Bear Killer,” was it? It caused the ceiling to crumble, and now there are numerous nicks and notches furrowing into the floor!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...I'm a dead man.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Did you at least remember to get the groceries, kupo?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I-I went! But I damned near threw my back out lugging the stuff around, so I had one of 'em spry fellas near the stalls haul 'em back for me.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That's not cunning...that's cheating.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But even if I were to return and get 'em m'self...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It'd be too late.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So you want to absolutely avoid heading home?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But if I don't bring you back, she'll scour my skin and skewer my sides!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Sorry, little friend, but I'm not doing it!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Kupo! Not entirely unexpected.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Your loving wife may lamentably leave you, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: B-but I don't want to spend the end of my days rotting alone!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
...Dare I entertain the thought?
Maybe if I had an alter ego...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: One of the academics from the Jeuno Institute of Magical Studies told me something when I received my scroll.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “The energies of Trust magic are a representation of the bonds of trust, friendship, and camaraderie between two individuals.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Perhaps...perhaps I should rethink my stance. If I can “serve” others, then so be it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Player Name≻! Steel yourself!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: How many times have we sparred, and how many times have you emerged the victor? If anyone has strong bonds with me, it would be you!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do you remember the trials the Magian Moogles gave? The ones you passed with flying colors?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Power comes from the gut, my ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[boy/girl]. And using a gut like yours, my alter ego would be able to withstand any sucker punch my wife throws its way!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: A stomach smacker? My tummy trembles at the thought, kupo...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You were also made to suffer the ill effects of “brown magic” as a bit of an...experiment.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: When you say it that way, it sounds so sordid.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But now you've got a liver of steel! My alter ego should be able to withstand any shots to the organs my honey might dish out!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There was also that time when I engaged in a fierce struggle with my eternal nemesis, Degenhard. Boy, you sure got caught up in our squabbles--but somehow remained unscathed.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I thought my aura would be too much for you to handle, but you pulled through by the skin of your teeth.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
...≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 1≻
That's not how it happened, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: My old lady's got a bit of a fire aura herself, so any alter ego I make with you can surely withstand the heat!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I also remember those “special eastern techniques” they put you through when you were frustrated with your limits once more.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I can still see the look on that old biddy Chamama's face when that...thing came out of you. Half disgust, half curiosity.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...I'd be careful about calling a budding beauty like her a “biddy.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Surely the alter ego we create will woo my wife into a lovelorn stupor!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: (She'd slap him silly if she saw his bluster and bravado, kupo...)≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This'll flare up some painful memories, but... Remember that infernal contract you signed?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The one with Atori-Tutori?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Far be it from me to use the term “lust for power,” but...well, you're a braver ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[man/woman] than I!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Beyond doubt, the alter ego we call into being will fear nothing--nor will it sweat the small stuff!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Such arrogant apologies would make her apoplectic, kupo...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And finally, do you remember when I gave you a little present?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: When the time comes, and I pass on...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I want you to take my hat, stand here in my place, and spread your wings.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But I don't cling to illusions. I know you want to go out there, adventure, and meet lots of ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[pretty young women/strapping young lads].≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Maybe...maybe I could join too, kupo?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Floating here is as boring as balancing boxes.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Mayhaps my alter ego'd be a help then...
His back would give out easily, though, so don't make it too tough on him! Heh heh.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
<Sigh>...
Such a base boor you can be...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'd hurry up, kupo. Maat's tremendously tired.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In any event. The bonds we share will surely cultivate something special!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
If you say no, then...≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 1≻
...then I've got to face the music.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And Maat was never deft at dancing, kupo.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Urk... Please! I'm begging you! Don't give up on me now!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Success, kupo!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We did it!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: All who face me are like guppies before a shark! Heh heh heh!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Positively peachy! Now you can turn the tides against your storming spouse!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: M-my...spouse...?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Go forth, my alter ego! I'm getting tired of sleeping in the doghouse!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: B-but what if she takes her wrath out on me!? Forget it, I'm not going!≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I knew it straight from the start, kupo!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Have heart, Maat! There are always ample supplies of adventurers!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
<Sigh>
I suppose you're right...after all, I've worked hard these long years.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Good luck with all your alter egos, ≺Player Name≻, and remember to never give up, no matter the cost!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Phew. When I agreed to get involved with the Trust initiative, I didn't imagine it to be so...trying.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hmmmmmm...
I was sure poring over these annals of history would be enough.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Oh ho? Do my eyes deceive me, or are you a Trust initiate?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Are you an initiate?
≺Selection Dialog≻No...
Uh, what are you doing?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: No? Then perhaps I need to take a break. I thought I read your magical aura properly, but my endless hours of study must have taken their toll.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Well, there was the one gentlewoman who claims to have called forth an alter ego all by herself.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Could you imagine what this means for our research? We may be on the verge of an incredible breakthrough!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Rumors say that intimate knowledge of the person she was trying to summon was sufficient to complete the ritual. So here I am, researching, trying to replicate her success with a historical figure.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But it's no good. Without the bonds, we just can't do it! The closest we've come is to craft ciphers--magical parchments that concentrate energies from a third party into physical forms. But that's the rub: it still requires those bonds in the first place.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But someday...someday...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Where are my manners? You didn't come here to hear a stuffy scholar's ramblings.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
And just look at you!≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 2≻
Fascinating...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Yes, your aura...≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 1≻
I've done it again, haven't I? A thousand pardons. I asked if you were part of the Trust initiative, but you are so much more than that.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Take this ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ as a gift from the institute. It's a cipher crafted from the very process I spoke of earlier.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The emotions of separate individuals converted into magical energy. Extraordinary, wouldn't you agree? Calling forth an alter ego with the thoughts of a third party.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It's all very experimental, so I make no promises as to the efficacy of such a scroll. It's all we can do to keep the energies from collapsing in on themselves.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Unlike a traditional scroll, these ciphers cannot be recited by anyone with a passing level of literacy. They require the assistance of certain institute staff located in major cities throughout Vana'diel.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Still, I promise the journey will be worth it...for you, and for us.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Bonds cannot be severed like a hot knife cutting through Selbina butter. The key is whether or not the strengths of the bonds' creators are enough to survive transcription.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If there's someone who you feel a strong connection with, what can it hurt to ask them for their cooperation? You'll never know until you try!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hello. Can I help you?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hm? You're here about ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻6≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'm sorry you came all this way, but I've already been briefed on that particular topic.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Wait just a moment. Ah, now I remember you. Yes, I've been looking for you ever since our last encounter. Now, I need you in the field to help with my research...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ah, forgive me. I was so excited to find the person I was looking for, I forgot to explain what it is I'm doing.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I've heard from a colleague that my research into Trust magic has earned the recognition of an academic organization.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: They have even given me clearance to read their most confidential documents in pursuit of my research. Well, a portion of them at least.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: However, when comparing that information against what I had gathered, I came across some interesting discoveries.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: For example, I learned that you had defeated an unusual life-form considered to be the physical embodiment of the darkest parts of a person's soul.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Then it struck me--a new line of thought in my Trust magic research.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That's right. I'm researching the topic of a dark Trust magic!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
How will you respond?
≺Selection Dialog≻Dark Trust magic?
I see where this is going.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Huh? You mean you don't know?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Oh you do, do you?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Well, allow me to briefly explain things just in case.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Currently, the Trust magic you use is based on light. It draws on positive forces such as trust, friendship, and ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[brotherly/sisterly] love.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: On the other hand, Trust magic based on darkness draws upon negative forces to generate its magic, much like how that woman was able to accomplish what she did.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Oh, I suppose I'm leaving out some rather important information. That is to say, an explanation of the negative aspects of mankind's darker side.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'm basically referring to things like apathy, arrogance, cowardice, envy, and rage. You know, the darkest parts of one's soul. I believe that everybody harbors these feelings, at least to a certain extent.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In a sense, all of us are united by the darkness within our souls. Therefore, it only seems logical to infer that we have the necessary conditions to employ Trust magic from it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: All that remains is to try and elevate the darkness within the alter ego's soul and somehow link up with it...a type of bond all its own.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Although, even if we are unable to utilize the Trust magic, we have the ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ at our disposal. Intimate knowledge of your quarry should enable you to form a bond with them.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Which brings me to my request. I'd like for you to test your mettle against those unique forces. However, it cannot be any regular fight. You must really get to know your opponent.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I requested the A.M.A.N. to create a Records of Eminence objective for this purpose, so it should help you remain cognizant of your opponent during battle.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hm? You want to know how to fight this particular opponent again? I think you probably know more about that sort of thing than I do.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You learn more about Trust magic, and I get further along in my research. That's what I call a “win-win.”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I heard from my colleague that he obtained a rather unusual cipher. Perhaps you should see this through to its conclusion?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ah, it's you again. It seems everything went rather well.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Judging by the magical aura you're giving off, I'd say we got the results I was hoping for.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Keep in mind that Trust magic research is an ongoing process. I must continue my efforts to unlock its mysteries.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'm working on preparations for my next study. Please come by again later.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hello again. I've finished making the necessary preparations. This is the data I'm searching for this time.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thanks again for your help.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If the test results for this darkness-based Trust magic follow my hypothesis, then my next step will be to research Trust magic that combines the power of both light and darkness.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I believe Trust magic that combines the power of light and darkness no longer just gives rise to alter egos, but a unique form of existence.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: An alter ego combining the power of both light and darkness... Just think of what this could mean!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Although, I'm currently suffering from a lack of research samples.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In order to successfully realize dark-based Trust magic, I tried replicating the connection that my research was based on, but it is not going so well...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If only I could get to the truth of the matter, it could be like a ticket to eternal paradise without the unfortunate precursor of dying first.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Rolandienne in Southern San d'Oria (G-10).≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Isakoth in Bastok Markets (E-11).≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Fhelm Jobeizat in Windurst Woods (J-10).≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Eternal Flame in Western Adoulin (H-11).≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Perhaps it would behoove you to speak with Nantoto in Lower Jeuno (H-8).≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Invisible eyes upon you cause the hairs on the back of your neck to rise.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text
