field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Wait but a moment.
Here, follow this command--er, compendium to the letter and you should be able to learn a thing or two.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Ah, this almost slipped my mind.
Should you receive any distinct sorts of artifacts for completing an objective, I will be happy to take them off your hands.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Worry not, for I am not out to rob you of your glory. Quite the opposite, in fact. I will provide you with a worthwhile reward for collecting them.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thanks to your donation, I now have ≺Numeric Parameter 1≻ ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Speaker Name≻)ａ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ in safekeeping.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ohohoho... Turning in sparks, I see.≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hold your hoarder hares, ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[hero/heroine]. I love your enthusiasm, but you're not going to learn a thing without a primer.
Ahhh, here it is. Have a look-see.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Oh, crud, that's right.
You should trade me any special artifacts you get from completing objectives.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
“Why?” What a good question!
Because I'll give you a nifty-difty reward at some point, that's why.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thanks for doing what I asked. Now I have a total of ≺Numeric Parameter 1≻ ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Speaker Name≻)ａ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ from you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You want to trrrade in sparks, do you?≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Let me wake up from my catnap first...≺Unknown Parameter (Type: 36) 1≻
Alright, now rrread this.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Wait, wait, wait!
If you happen to get any purrrticularly interesting items from completing objectives, send them my way.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Don't worry, I'm as honest as a cat when the meat's out of reach. I thought of taking them all for myself...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...but I don't want to make fur fly with the Adventurers' Mutual Aid Network, so I'll do my job like a good little kitty.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Grrreat! Now I have ≺Numeric Parameter 1≻ ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Speaker Name≻)ａ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ from you. Thanks!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Hm?
Oh, spark exchange... Of course.≺Possible Special Code: 00≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I'm not completely sure, but this might help set some things straight...I guess.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Let me add one thing.
Please find it within your heart of hearts to give me anything of particular interest you get from completing objectives.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
I'll make it worth your while...I swear!
Just keep at it and I'll be sure to surprise you with a hot, steaming helping of gratitude one day.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Thanks for doing your part in the battle for love and peace! With this latest addition, I'm now keeping track of ≺Numeric Parameter 1≻ ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Speaker Name≻)ａ≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ for you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Records of Eminence is a system brought to you by the caring folks at the Adventurers' Mutual Aid Network. Set your own objectives whenever you desire, and fulfill them to receive compensation.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “To set these tasks, select 'Objective List' from the Quests menu, then choose ones that suit your fancy.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “You will be rewarded with gil and sparks of eminence, which serve the same function as points, notes, credits, and other such methods of quantifying one's greatness. As an extra incentive, adventurers will earn three times the amount of sparks for completing an objective the first time.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Completed objectives will vanish from your quest list unless they are repeatable. In the event that you wish to make room for different objectives, you will need to remove them manually.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “As a corollary regarding rewards, you'll be blessed with special remuneration once you complete several objectives. Bask in the joy of these pleasant surprises when you can.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Lastly, any and all acts of vandalism directed against your ≺Possible Special Code: 01≻≺Possible Special Code: 05≻3≺BAD CHAR: 8280≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻≺BAD CHAR: 80≻ are strictly prohibited.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

Is the ≺Multiple Choice (Parameter 39)≻[/Argosy Armor/Hesychast's Attire/Piety Attire/Archmage's Attire/Vitiation Attire/Plunderer's Attire/Caballarius Armor/Fallen's Armor/Ankusa Armor/Bihu Attire/Arcadian Attire/Sakonji Armor/Mochizuki Garb/Pteroslaver Armor/Glyphic Attire/Luhlaza Attire/Lanun Attire/Pitre Attire/Horos Attire/Pedagogy Attire/Bagua Attire/Futhrak Attire] okay?

No.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Why I never! One with such a meager aura is not fit to be in my presence, let alone speak to me!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Well, it took you long enough to come speak with me! I have been sending furtive glances your way for what seems like an eternity now!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You know, you really should give up on helping Jamal with his utterly pointless research.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Like everything he does, it is destined to end in abject failure.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hm? What do you mean it is none of my business?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do you know who you are speaking to? I am Marjory, the most brilliant magician this realm has ever seen, and the foremost expert on Trust research!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I am somewhat surprised you did not already know that. At any rate, there is a certain matter I need your help with.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text:
Will you help her?
≺Selection Dialog≻Sure.
No thanks.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: H-how dare you decline my offer... You will come to regret this, I assure you!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I am pleased to see you make such a wise decision! Hehe... I cannot wait to see that buffoon Jamal choke on his own words!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Now then! Jamal likes to equate the darkness of alter egos to the root of all evil or some such nonsense, but as with most things, he could not be more wrong.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: These are just my thoughts on the issue, but...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You see, unlike Jamal, I do not believe that Trust magic is something meant to be cast outwards from its user.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: No, Trust magic is designed to look within us. In other words...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The alter egos take shape due to the power contained within a kind of unseen pipeline inside of us that conveys our feelings and thoughts to them.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That got me thinking! If one could somehow boost the amount of those feelings and thoughts being sent...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It could lead to the alter ego itself becoming even more powerful!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hm? What do you mean you don't understand? You really are quite dense, aren't you?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Well, I am stuck with you, I guess, so you will need a few things if you are to help me with my research.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: First of all, you will need this special diamond.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is capable of detecting the feelings and thoughts you direct at the alter ego you are summoning.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: This diamond then stores them within its crystalline confines.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Once it has gathered a certain amount of thoughts and feelings, it will change color.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: So basically, I need you to use your Trust magic until you see the diamond change color!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: To help you to that end, I have also prepared something else for you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I ordered the A.M.A.N. to provide you with a list of Records of Eminence objectives!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There are three objectives for you to complete. You simply need to complete them all to collect what is necessary!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ah, that reminds me. No matter what, you must not lose this diamond.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is made from an extremely rare gemstone, so I forced my mother's jewelry shop to let me have it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It was originally a rather unusual diamond that changed color whenever it sensed a change in the surrounding temperature.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I simply used a little magic to make some key improvements and recreate something from a legend I once heard in a faraway land!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Now then, let us begin the experiment!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ah, there you are! I was expecting you much sooner. Hurry up and hand me the diamond already.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Hmm... Very well done. You have collected just the right amount of thoughts and feelings. Now, for just a touch of magic...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I-it's a staggering success! The thoughts have been imbued into the diamond!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Listen carefully. You simply need to use this diamond as a catalyst when invoking your Trust magic.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: When you do, the thoughts sent to your alter ego when it manifests will be made even more powerful.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: That power will then be sent to the alter ego when you attempt to call upon it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: As a result, the alter ego itself will also become stronger!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: However, there is one thing you need to be careful of.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The more of these pipelines you use to call forth the alter egos, the weaker the effect of the catalyst will become.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I can see that your feeble mind is not comprehending what I am saying. Let me see, how can I dumb this down so even you can understand it...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: If your party is made up of you and five alter egos, that means that five pipelines will be used, so each alter ego will only be slightly powered up.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And if your party contains you and one other member, along with four alter egos, that means there would be four alter ego pipelines and each one will be a little stronger.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Finally, if there are five in your party along with only one alter ego, that means there is also only one alter ego pipeline, so it will be made considerably stronger.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Do you understand now? Yes? I am glad to hear it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Take note that the catalyst will not be effective unless you yourself are of considerable strength.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Perhaps consider starting with a simple greeting. Something like...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: “Hello, everyone. My name's ≺Player Name≻. Nice to meet you!”≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Of course, injecting your own personal flavor may act as a conversation starter and help people to remember you.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: No matter which route you choose, make sure to always remain polite. There is no better way to start a friendship off on the right foot.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: When speaking with others, it's critical to listen and be mindful of what they say.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Always talking and never listening may come across as rude.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Another important point is to always be mindful of the listener. How would you feel if someone said that to you? Think carefully before sending someone a message.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It also helps to be clear and concise.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Being vague might cause others to get the wrong impression.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Be extremely careful when giving out personal information such as your address or telephone number.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Furthermore, refrain from making disparaging or aggressive remarks.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Once you are close to someone, you may be more comfortable letting your hair down, but it is strongly recommended that you refrain from any actions that may be construed as harassment.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: After joining a linkshell, you may find that you have difficulty participating in conversation or that your personality is too different from the other members.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: One of your options in such a situation is to inform the linkshell leader and then leave.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Finding a linkshell that is the perfect fit might not always be easy, but there is certainly a group out there that will match your feelings and goals.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Once you find those kinds of friends, hold them fast and value them as much as they value you. There is no better way to enjoy life in Vana'diel.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Lord/Lady] ≺Player Name≻, please forgive my hasty departure earlier. I have had some time to reflect on my journey here...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It is about the Emptiness threatening to consume my land.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I surmise that it is intimately connected to this destructive force that threatens to claim the future, just as Gilgamesh was telling me in Norg.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The Emptiness will have doubtlessly spread from the Far East, its tendrils stretching ever westward.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Lord/Lady] ≺Player Name≻, forgive me...would that I had been stronger...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: But you know what it means for me to be standing before you here.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Lord/Lady] ≺Player Name≻, you know what it means for me to be standing before you here.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I must confess to stationing one of my agents around the area after our soiree in Norg.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It was not for any nefarious purpose, I assure you--it was merely to gather what information I could about the destruction of the future.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: And as I implied earlier, the Emptiness is almost certainly the cause of Iroha's claims.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Lord/Lady] ≺Player Name≻, the Emptiness ceased to encroach when Prishe and her companions toppled Promathia.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Something horrific must have happened for it to rear its head once more.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I would ask Iroha to tell me what she knows.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Forgive me for keeping you waiting, Master.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Sir Tenzen, the pleasure is mine.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I am so glad to see you again.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Again? But this is the first time we...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Ah, but of course. You mean to say that you have met me in the future.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You are the very reason I am able to stand here today. My tears flowed like rain when last we parted.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ...You mean to say that I was swallowed up in the Emptiness.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Not just you. Everyone.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I thought myself better prepared for this. So such a future does come to pass.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Then that means...I failed.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Sir Tenzen, lift your head.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: In my era, you and the master were revered as heroes of the highest caliber.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: It was not any failure on your behalf. When darkness poured forth from the crystal, there was nothing you could have done to stop it.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Secluded on that small island, I was unable to stem the rising tide, and the world was torn asunder...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Heavens be good...≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: There is only one thing we can do.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: The question that remains...is why?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Has some nefarious new force arisen to force open the Gates of Paradise?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Or is there another threatening to absorb the power of the crystals for its own vile ends?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Neither you nor Master shared with me the particulars.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Strife descended upon us in but an instant. Umbral energies radiated from the crystal, and the world was wrapped in gloom before we had a chance to draw breath.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: You mean that we were obliterated into the darkness without knowing why?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Or was there a reason why we could not tell you?≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: I fear the plot will continue to thicken.≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: Then there is only one thing to do!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: We must protect our world!≺Prompt≻
field.Attribute:name: text

field.Element:Text: ≺Multiple Choice (Player Gender)≻[Lord/Lady] ≺Player Name≻, Lady Iroha.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: The future is ours for the taking, and I swear to fight until I have drawn my last breath!≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: Wh-what!?≺Possible Special Code: 00≻

field.Element:Text: Would that it were sufficient...but the light remains ever pale.≺Prompt≻

field.Element:Text: You have yet to meet with Lady Prishe, correct?≺Prompt≻
